data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This spacious two-story house is nestled on a meticulously landscaped lot, boasting a lush backyard with a generous deck area. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a well-appointed, chef's delight large kitchen, perfect for cooking and entertaining. The main floor also features a dedicated study, providing a quiet oasis for work or study. The formal dining room is ready to host your most special gatherings and celebrations. The game room is a hub of recreational fun, offering endless entertainment possibilities. For movie nights and immersive entertainment experiences, the media room is the ideal spot, complete with a large screen and comfortable seating.  Downstairs you'll find a spacious primary bedroom suite with jet tub and huge closet.  This property is the perfect combination of style, comfort, and functionality, designed to cater to your every need. Don't miss this opportunity to make this house your home sweet home!
